### HOW TO REVIEW, UPDATE OR DELETE YOUR DATA

Open the App → **Settings › Privacy & Data** or send an e-mail to **[privacy@ambigram.app](mailto:privacy@ambigram.app)** with your request.  We’ll guide you through verification and fulfil it unless restricted by law.

